{
  "texts": [
    "Virtual tokens are added to the beginning of the decoder.",
    "Based on the design of chunked crossattention, left padding is added to ensure the length of input (virtual tokens + context + question) is a multiple of chunk size.",
    "Adapter and LoRA layers are in all attention layers in both transformer architectures.",
    "This means that for RETRO they are also inserted in the retrieval encoder which receives retrieved neighbors.",
    "We provide additional hyperparameter tuning, resource utilization and prompt template details in Appendix A."
  ]
}